.SH "FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS - Contact Information"
This document contains frequently asked questions submitted to JASSPA. Use the
E-Mail reflector and associated logs, described in the
.Hl "Contact Information" Contact - 
section, alternatively questions may be submitted to:-
.IP
\fCEmail:support@jasspa.com\fR
.LP
We cannot  promise to resolve all questions, but will endeavor to answer most.
We would also  appreciate  comments on how to improve the  readability  of the
documentation   or   suggestions   for   improvements   where  you  think  the
documentation is deficient.
