.ds Qu "Icons are not displayed correctly in Microsoft Windows environments !!
.ds Qn 04
.NH faq\*(Qn page "FAQ(\*(Qn) \- \*(Qu"
.XI faq\*(Qn 0f "\*(Qu"
.ne 10
.SH "QUESTION (\*(Qn)"
\*(Qu
.SH ANSWER
After installing on Microsoft  platforms, the Icons in the Explorer window may
not be showing correctly. To remedy the situation then the following steps may
be taken.
.IP "\fBWindows '95\fR"
Try  re-starting  the  system  first. If the  icons are still  incorrect  then
re-start in Safe mode and delete the file:
.IP
\fCc:\\windows\\ShellIconCache\fR
.IP
Restart and the Icons should be correct.
.IP "\fBWindow '98\fR"
Try  re-starting  the  system  first. If the  Icons are still  incorrect  then
re-start  in Safe  mode,  this  should  re-generate  the Icon  cache.  Restart
windows.
.IP "\fBNT\fR"
Restart the system.
.LP
