.NH faq\*(Qn page "FAQ(\*(Qn) \- \*(Qu"
.XI faq\*(Qn 0f "\*(Qu"
.ne 10
.SH "QUESTION (\*(Qn)"
\*(Qu
.SH ANSWER
For  windows  '95 up  until  OEM  service  release  2, the  OS  could  not
distinguish the difference between the files:-
.CS
\.xxx
\.xxx~
