spaces. Alternatively disable \fBtab\fR mode for all file type using
.Ht user-setup 3
i.e.
.IP
\fBHelp\fR -> \fBUser Setup\fR -> \fBGeneral\fR -> \fBTab\fR
.SS "To re-enable the <tab> key"
